<paragraph blockId="3.[178,1086,654,852]" pageId="3" pageNumber="662">
M a l e g e n i t a l i a. Median lobe of aedeagus in lateral view (
<figureCitation box="[927,1019,654,676]" captionStart="Figs 6-10" captionStartId="9.[178,218,894,914]" captionTargetBox="[183,1079,227,876]" captionTargetId="figure-2@9.[178,1085,220,884]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="Figs 6-10: Feronia laticollis CHAUDOIR, lectotype: Fig. (6) aedeagus, left lateral view; Fig. (7) aedeagus, right lateral view; Fig. (8) apex of aedeagus, dorsal view; Fig. (9) right paramere, internal view; Fig. (10) right paramere, external view. Scale bar 0.5 mm (6-10)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5332864" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5332864/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="662">Figs 6-7</figureCitation>
) with ostium deflected to left; apical part longer than basal part, with ventral margin slightly concave distally and apex somewhat bent downwards; basal part with strongly developed and prominent ventral process; internal sac (non-inverted state) with indistinct chitinised piece. Apex of median lobe dorsally (
<figureCitation box="[574,637,772,794]" captionStart="Figs 6-10" captionStartId="9.[178,218,894,914]" captionTargetBox="[183,1079,227,876]" captionTargetId="figure-2@9.[178,1085,220,884]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="Figs 6-10: Feronia laticollis CHAUDOIR, lectotype: Fig. (6) aedeagus, left lateral view; Fig. (7) aedeagus, right lateral view; Fig. (8) apex of aedeagus, dorsal view; Fig. (9) right paramere, internal view; Fig. (10) right paramere, external view. Scale bar 0.5 mm (6-10)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5332864" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5332864/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="662">Fig. 8</figureCitation>
) straight with tip slightly deflected to left. Left paramere (
<figureCitation box="[336,435,801,823]" captionStart="Figs 6-10" captionStartId="9.[178,218,894,914]" captionTargetBox="[183,1079,227,876]" captionTargetId="figure-2@9.[178,1085,220,884]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="Figs 6-10: Feronia laticollis CHAUDOIR, lectotype: Fig. (6) aedeagus, left lateral view; Fig. (7) aedeagus, right lateral view; Fig. (8) apex of aedeagus, dorsal view; Fig. (9) right paramere, internal view; Fig. (10) right paramere, external view. Scale bar 0.5 mm (6-10)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5332864" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5332864/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="662">Figs 9-10</figureCitation>
) sickle-shaped; basal part longer than apical one, forming widened bulb; apical part with pointed tip.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[178,1085,867,1036]" pageId="3" pageNumber="662">
